text: Paulo Jamur (born 17 December 1964) is a Brazilian former cyclist. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Brazil Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
